{"tid":2225304,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"蜆殼計劃全球裁員最多9,000人","createTime":"2020-10-01T08:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T09:21:34.000Z","uid":185631,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50b97134e166f7d9cc9129adc5dbdbcf46988f14","tid":2225304,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:16:15.000Z","msg":"據《BBC》報道，蜆殼計劃在全球裁員7,000至9,000人，因疫情爆發導致全球石油需求急跌，預計裁員將會於2022年進行，當中包括1,500名參與自願離職計劃的員工。<br />\n<br />\n蜆殼首財季盈利下跌46%至29億美元，第財二季更倒退82%至6.38億美元，預計第三財季盈利將介乎8億至8.75億美元之間的下限。目前公司正致力削減成本，相信至2022年每年將節省20億至25億美元。<br />\n<br />\n***************************************<br />\n<br />\n蜆殼石油公司（SHELL）全球性裁員，美裡的員工是否也受波及，備受關注。<br />\n<br />\n根據彭博社，由於布倫特原油價格已接近年初價格的一半，荷蘭皇家殼牌石油公司正計劃向一些員工提供自願遣散費。<br />\n<br />\n殼牌首席執行官本范伯登在給員工的說明中說，這家荷蘭石油巨頭正在努力變得更精簡，更具韌性。<br />\n<br />\n文中提到，鑒於油價走勢和需求不確定性，殼牌自1945年以來月首次削減股息，該公司將重新設計其組織，以適應不同的未來並變得更加強大。<br />\n<br />\n這次的石油價格危機帶來不小的影響，尤其是美裡作為國內其中一個產油地，很多商家都供應物資到岸外油井，對美裡的經濟勢必帶來一定的衝擊，尤其是石油業的員工，是消費力很強的一群 ，一旦失去這些消費者，奢侈品市場會更縮小。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-con/now.1046577/latest-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-con%2Fnow.1046577%2Flatest-news&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w15ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=ffd52ea8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-con/now.1046577/latest-news</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/index.php/news/east-malaysia/2020/05/23/342223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientaldaily.com.my%2Findex.php%2Fnews%2Feast-malaysia%2F2020%2F05%2F23%2F342223&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w15ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=2a3ae671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.orientaldaily.com.my/index.php/news/east-malaysia/2020/05/23/342223</a>"},{"pid":"c04ce7cf62d9fe5b8409773d7ad692a0605c4713","tid":2225304,"uid":101945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:17:00.000Z","msg":"#多謝shell  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b8c59fd36b286a13a281bb2dd5dcdbdf904076","tid":2225304,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:21:43.000Z","msg":"股價升定跌"},{"pid":"f0fc199685247b70ba6708e83295feb49249517e","tid":2225304,"uid":60527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90b8c59fd36b286a13a281bb2dd5dcdbdf904076","tid":2225304,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:21:43.000Z","msg":"股價升定跌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T08:48:53.000Z","msg":"Cut cost，升<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afbb88b2ad3a9e744888706d2bb2c1c2a2a7204d","tid":2225304,"uid":35323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T09:21:34.000Z","msg":"屌, 香港有減到油價?"}]}